strings: <voice_0x01000ADD><se_high>Accuracy: It says yes! what do you have planned for her
<voice_0x01000ADE><se_low>January: We spoke with the president here.
<voice_0x01000ADF><se_high>Accuracy: not the army? I'd love to hear.
<voice_0x01000AE0><se_high>Accuracy: It has nothing to do with the governor. you are completely different what is it?
<voice_0x01000AE2><se_low>January: "Meet the President" is an epic tale of laughter, emotion and tears...
<voice_0x01000AE3><se_high>Accuracy: indeed? Why are you setting me on fire?
<voice_0x01000AE4><se_low>January: just do it! It all started on a beautiful summer day...with so much passion...
<voice_0x01000AE5><se_low>January: I decided to take a break. The old bad guys can attack.
<voice_0x01000AE6><se_low>January: So I decided to leave my hometown and start all over again.
